data.description: HUNT CREST ESTATES IN TOWSON!!!  4 Bedrooms, 2 Full / 1 Half  Bathrooms, 3 Levels, Dutch Colonial Styling,  Attached Garage, Multi-Car Driveway Parking, Private .93 Acre Park-Like Setting w/Fantastic Views, Rear Yard w/Concrete Patio and Lots of Room to Run and Play for Humans and Animals, All Appliances Included, Gas Heat and Central Air, Public Water and Sewer, Voluntary Community Association (Chatterleigh Association) and Fun and Friendly Neighborhood Events, Excellent Location for Easy Access to Area Amenities and Popular Places, including: Loch Raven Reservoir and Cromwell Valley Park, as well as: Interstate 695, Interstate 95, Towson Business District, Baltimore, MARC Train, BWI Airport, More!!!**MORE PPROPERTY DETAILS:  MAIN LEVEL: Front Entry Foyer, Formal Living Room, Formal Dining Room, Remodeled Kitchen w/42” Cabinets, Granite Counters and Breakfast Bar, Stainless Steel Appliances: Natural Gas Range/Oven, Refrigerator w/Ice Maker, and Under Cabinet Dishwasher, Pantry Closet, and Glass Sliders to Rear Concrete Patio, Family Room off the Kitchen w/Wood-Burning Fireplace w/Mantle, Main Level Powder Room, and Main Level Laundry w/Utility Sink and Garage Access**UPPER LEVEL:  4 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms, Spacious Primary Bedroom w/Full Bathroom and Walk-In Closet, All 4 Bedrooms have Hardwood Floors, Hallway Full Bathroom**LOWER LEVEL: Full Basement w/Rear Outside Entrance, Recreation Areas, Mechanicals Area w/Natural Gas Furnace and Hot Water Heater, Storage/Workshop Area, and Space for Additional Finished Rooms**EXTERIOR: Beautiful Views, Fantastic Yard Space, .93 Acre Setting w/Shade Trees, Beautiful Rhododendrons, and Invisible Fencing, Rear Concrete Patio, Multi-Car Parking Area and Attached Garage (23x13), Shed**UTILITIES: Natural Gas and Electric Service through BGE, Public Water and Sewer Service, Natural Gas Fired Furnace and Water Heater, Forced Air Heat and Central Air Conditioning**RECENT UPDATES INCLUDE: Kitchen, Roof, Rear Concrete Patio, Asphalt Driveway, TRANE Furnace and Central Air Conditioning System, Hot Water Heater, and Main Level Flooring**OTHER: Room for Living Area or Garage Space Expansion**AREA SCHOOLS: Hampton Elementary, Ridgely Middle, Loch Raven High**SHOWINGS: By Appointment - Seller Notice Required but EASY-TO-SEE**CONTRACT / SETTLEMENT:  A Quick Settlement (sooner the better but within 30 Days) is Available**MORE!!!
